Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.45,0:02:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The time is the Great Pirate Era.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.42,0:02:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Countless pirates fight \Ndesperately for the One Piece,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.62,0:02:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,the great treasure left behind\Nby Gold Roger, the Pirate King.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.23,0:02:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Monkey D. Luffy, a boy\Nwhose body turned to rubber
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.13,0:03:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,after he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.07,0:03:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,also takes to the sea\Nto become the next Pirate King.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.97,0:03:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,As Luffy and his friends\Novercome numerous adventures,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.91,0:03:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,the World Government is less and less\Nable to ignore their existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.88,0:03:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,This is exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.31,0:03:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of adventure \Nis waiting for us next?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.58,0:03:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The crew, on its way to the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.72,0:03:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,will speed along the Grand Line again today!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.03,0:03:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,After losing his brother Ace during \Nthe Paramount War against the Navy,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.20,0:03:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy was consumed with unbearable sorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.84,0:03:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,However, 10 years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.21,0:03:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Ace, Sabo and Luffy were competing
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.18,0:03:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,to hunt the big tiger to \Ndecide who would be captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.78,0:03:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,They met a former pirate \N- Naguri who knew Roger,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.85,0:04:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,and he agreed to give Luffy \Ntips on how to become a pirate.
