Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.05,0:04:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you always do that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.95,0:04:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You always attack so openly!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.59,0:04:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! What about you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.22,0:05:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That was horrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.29,0:05:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's put some poisonous \Nmushrooms in the bait tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.52,0:05:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.73,0:05:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,He's big but still a member \Nof the cat family...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.60,0:05:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That means catnip might work, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.10,0:05:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.01,0:05:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder how Luffy is doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.88,0:05:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a week since he left the hideout.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.55,0:05:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,We should have gone to see him by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.78,0:05:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You know how he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.49,0:05:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe the training is too hard for him \Nand he's crying "I wanna go home!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.36,0:05:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Maybe he's dead already!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.64,0:05:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.64,0:06:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you care about Luffy? \NHe's your younger brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.92,0:06:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! I don't care if \Nhe's crying or he's dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.49,0:06:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn! Stop being stubborn already!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.12,0:06:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You must...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.03,0:06:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow, ow, ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.53,0:06:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.10,0:06:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.84,0:06:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay? Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.38,0:06:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,--Luffy!\N--Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.58,0:06:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Ace! Sabo! Long time no see!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.62,0:06:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,How've you been?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.35,0:06:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, well, you know.
