Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.36,0:06:57.10,"Sign",,0,0,0,,"Tiger"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.56,0:06:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that? A target?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.37,0:06:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Sabo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.60,0:07:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna show you the result of my training!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.61,0:07:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.41,0:07:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.04,0:07:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,...Pistol!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.66,0:07:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.83,0:07:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That's awesome! You couldn't \Nreach that far a week ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.43,0:07:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you beat that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.07,0:07:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.00,0:07:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of tips did you give him?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.91,0:07:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing special.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.27,0:07:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,He was just chopping wood \Nwith an ax for me everyday.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.08,0:07:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But maybe it helped him \Nbuild up his physique.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.12,0:07:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me have a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.99,0:07:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We challenged Roger, the Pirate King, to a fight!
