Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.64,0:08:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean Roger?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.15,0:08:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt frustrated for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.65,0:08:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But I lost because I wasn't strong enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.92,0:08:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I rather feel grateful to him now.
