Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.14,0:08:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead and cut my head off! But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.91,0:08:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Please spare my crew in exchange for my head!
