Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.76,0:09:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,He was a man of quite high caliber!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.20,0:09:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.70,0:09:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't lie! There are dozens \Nof people who hate him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.31,0:09:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Do they really fight with Roger?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.21,0:09:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,In the world of pirates, when you \Nlose a fight, you lose your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.22,0:09:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.29,0:09:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's say that those people fought him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.22,0:09:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Just think. They can talk about \Ntheir grudges because they're alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.13,0:09:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get stronger and...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.63,0:09:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what if Roger had a son?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.17,0:09:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be hard to be his son.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.74,0:09:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether he chooses to live a \Nnormal life or as a pirate,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.22,0:10:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,he will always be haunted \Nby his father's name.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.69,0:10:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be quite hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.99,0:10:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,If I were his son, I wouldn't \Nwant to become a pirate.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.09,0:10:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Because that father's name would \Nruin his son's life in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.66,0:10:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,"Ruin his son's life"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.03,0:10:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop talking nonsense! \NYou don't know anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.30,0:10:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you fight me, old man?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.94,0:10:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.48,0:10:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I said, when you lose a \Nfight, you lose your life...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.58,0:10:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not gonna lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.24,0:10:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I win!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.97,0:10:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit! Do anything you like with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.31,0:11:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, I want you to come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.38,0:11:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.02,0:11:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.52,0:11:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know that there was a cove here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.83,0:11:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Guys! Hurry up and get over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.07,0:11:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Guys! Guys! Hustle, hustle!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.67,0:11:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want, Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.07,0:11:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be shocked!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.31,0:11:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.68,0:11:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,...boat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.05,0:11:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it cool?! It's a real pirate ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.89,0:11:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,A pirate ship?! Is this what \NNaguri has been making?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.63,0:11:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It will take forever to make it on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.20,0:11:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you two give me a hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.77,0:12:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,--Huh?\N--Give you a hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.74,0:12:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You said that I can do \Nanything I like with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.38,0:12:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,W-W-Wait a minute! I have to help, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.15,0:12:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You happened to be here, so.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.31,0:12:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not making any sense!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.25,0:12:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We're busy hunting the big tiger!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.92,0:12:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I can give you some pointers \Nto hunt the tiger.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.16,0:12:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Well, then maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.86,0:12:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me ask you a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.76,0:12:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you gonna do with the ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.84,0:12:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna go out to sea, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.80,0:12:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,\NTo find my crew that got split up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.17,0:12:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,To sea?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.98,0:12:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What? An old man can't go out to sea?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.31,0:12:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I wasn't gonna say that, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.65,0:12:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter how old \Nyou are to chase a dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.89,0:12:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care what anyone says, \NI'm gonna go out to sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.12,0:12:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already decided!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.79,0:12:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have a problem with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.33,0:12:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.10,0:13:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You're an old man, full of energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.37,0:13:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Ace?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.54,0:13:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,A promise is a promise. I'll \Ngive you a hand. And...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.31,0:13:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,...I will defeat you tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.38,0:13:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.99,0:13:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And so began their training \Nto be pirates with Naguri.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.36,0:13:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Through hard labor on the ship,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.60,0:13:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,they gained strength and honed their \Nskills by fighting with Naguri...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.74,0:13:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,...growing both physically and mentally.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.87,0:13:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Seasons come and go but spring comes late in Gray Terminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.22,0:14:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,--I'm gonna win today!\N--I'm not gonna lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.29,0:14:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna win!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.00,0:14:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.77,0:14:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,...Pistol!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.84,0:14:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.91,0:14:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Luffy! You did it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.15,0:14:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.38,0:14:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Boy, you guys are only thinking \Nabout getting stronger but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.32,0:14:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,...you think that's enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.22,0:14:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.06,0:14:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The strongest one among \Nus will become captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.86,0:14:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So what do you think about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.93,0:14:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! The one that kill the tiger!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.73,0:14:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The tiger, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.60,0:14:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, a captain needs to be \Nstrong - that's for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.94,0:14:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But there is more important thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.64,0:14:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,A more important thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.05,0:14:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, and that is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.09,0:15:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.03,0:15:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that? How disappointing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.03,0:15:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Easy, easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.87,0:15:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I didn't know that \Nyou were here, Ace-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.91,0:16:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.65,0:16:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What does it take to be a captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.25,0:16:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What is more important than being strong?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.12,0:16:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.96,0:16:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.36,0:16:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.50,0:16:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,To tell you the truth, I don't know it yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.37,0:16:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't a good captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.51,0:16:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But my crew,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.14,0:16:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,they called me "Captain" \Nuntil the last minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.35,0:16:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of that, I'm still the \Ncaptain of the Naguri Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.95,0:16:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Only your crew's approval \Ncan make you a captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.79,0:16:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Or something like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.10,0:16:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That's corny.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.44,0:17:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! It's done!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.62,0:17:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We did it, Naguri!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.42,0:17:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Cool! It's awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.89,0:17:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't have done it \Nwithout your help. Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.36,0:17:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really grateful!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.70,0:17:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, Naguri, are you setting sail soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.50,0:17:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. But before that, I have \Nto wrap up your training.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.27,0:17:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go and hunt the big tiger today!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.91,0:17:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.18,0:17:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna kill him and \Nend this stupid training!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.15,0:17:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.95,0:17:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget about me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.36,0:18:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Here he comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.07,0:18:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,There he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.48,0:18:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I go first!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.75,0:18:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,How predictable!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.20,0:18:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,How's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.47,0:18:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You're unguarded!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.64,0:18:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You gotta fight me now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.18,0:18:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop resisting, just give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.09,0:19:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Sabo! Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.53,0:19:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,D-D-Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.87,0:19:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Gum-Gum Pistol!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.74,0:19:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no! Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.08,0:19:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.13,0:19:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Ace! Sabo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.30,0:19:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So heavy! How powerful he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.10,0:19:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn! We're not good enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.17,0:19:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Only your crew's approval \Ncan make you a captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.71,0:19:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But we can't lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.01,0:20:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Guys, give me a hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.78,0:20:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's getting interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.19,0:20:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not fast enough but we \Ncan do it with Luffy's power!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.16,0:20:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Sabo, do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.50,0:20:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! Hey, tiger! Look over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.04,0:20:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiss my ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.11,0:20:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,--Luffy!\N--Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.61,0:20:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Pull it as much as you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.78,0:20:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Sabo, this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.52,0:20:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't! He's gonna eat me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.49,0:20:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do it, Sabo! \NLure him as far as you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.00,0:20:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you ready, Luffy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.97,0:20:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.60,0:20:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.17,0:20:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,...Rocket!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.33,0:21:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.93,0:21:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,So, Ace is gonna be our captain after all?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.74,0:21:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I worked so hard for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.04,0:21:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it up, Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.87,0:21:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.18,0:21:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. I'm not gonna become captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.18,0:21:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.98,0:21:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I didn't beat \Nthe tiger all by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.59,0:21:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.09,0:21:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I mean,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.66,0:21:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna make you guys \Nbeg me to become captain sometime soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.93,0:21:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you gonna beg him?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.16,0:21:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hell no!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.20,0:21:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.17,0:22:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like everything \Nturned out for the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.08,0:22:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright then...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.98,0:22:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.91,0:22:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time I see you, I'm gonna defeat you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.68,0:22:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep winning until then!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.29,0:22:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.96,0:22:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.49,0:22:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be waiting for you out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.98,0:22:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Thus, they said goodbye to Naguri
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.58,0:22:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,and Luffy and the other two \Nreturned to life on their own.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.29,0:23:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you know where he is, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.00,0:23:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. You don't have to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.57,0:23:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about time now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.54,0:23:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Call and tell his father that we found...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.11,0:23:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,...Sabo.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.95,0:23:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Sabo makes a difficult \Ndecision in order to save
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.45,0:23:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Ace and Luffy, who are being held hostage.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.79,0:23:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,But Sabo is overwhelmed by the suffocating
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.66,0:23:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,lifestyle in High Town.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.89,0:23:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, as if to deal the final blow, \Nyet another scheme is revealed...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.63,0:23:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, on One Piece:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.10,0:23:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,"Stolen Freedom!\NThe Nobles' Trap Closing in on the Brothers"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.70,0:23:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be the Pirate King!!
